# SASS INSTALLATION VIA NODE PACKAGE MANAGER (npm)

1. Install node
   Instruction: Go to <https://nodejs.org> and download/install the latest LTS version.

2. Install Sass global

   ```bash
   npm install -g sass
   ```

3. Verify Installation

   ```bash
   sass --version
   ```

   You should see something like 1.89.0 or similar
